{"tid":1422253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"石崗草堆內驚現手榴彈 證實為玩具","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:56:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3b192f62d766edf460008e2b7c0b1dec70b8d723","tid":1422253,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190806/photo/bkn-20190806103846337-0806_00822_001_05b.jpg?20190806151910\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190806%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190806103846337-0806_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20190806151910&h=70f2fcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上9時43分，水務署工人在石崗甲龍清除雜草期間，發現一個疑似手榴彈，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場封鎖一段山路，初步檢視是一個戰時手榴彈，已經通知爆炸品處理課到場處理，消防員亦在場戒備。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190806/photo/bkn-20190806103846337-0806_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190806151910\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190806%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190806103846337-0806_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190806151910&h=c0cfaeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190806/large/1565062822_28ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190806%2Flarge%2F1565062822_28ab.jpg&h=c7f18d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆炸品處理課人員到場檢視後，發現手榴彈為一枚黑色塑膠的玩具手榴彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為被泥掩蓋而引起誤會，證實虛驚一場，將玩具手榴彈檢走後收隊離去。"},{"pid":"d97682b2383ffc660c67c1298847269e82028fd3","tid":1422253,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190708/large/1562566136_7847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190708%2Flarge%2F1562566136_7847.jpg&h=282190a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳新巴站驚現「67式木柄手榴彈」木盒 警列發現財物案跟進<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301706</a>"},{"pid":"fd092c7e6a8d0a985ddafc0b98327af2225c2989","tid":1422253,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"邊個咁大整蠱??"},{"pid":"4701b5336d04dfab2f9aad3fec4eaa7777c4d5d8","tid":1422253,"uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"發現該「戰時手榴彈」為一塑膠製、比例一比一的玩具拔針式手榴彈，由於顏色為黑色，沾滿泥濘幾可亂真，現場隨即解封，玩具手榴彈由警員撿走。<br />\n<br />\nthis?<br />\n<img src=\"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2018/411/312/9648213114_471003456.220x220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbu01.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fibank%2F2018%2F411%2F312%2F9648213114_471003456.220x220.jpg&h=8d0febc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQnTHyEjjJ5wBpTaUily4SspbZ64ZM9L6jX1BDk8vKuRHPzBtdyUw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQnTHyEjjJ5wBpTaUily4SspbZ64ZM9L6jX1BDk8vKuRHPzBtdyUw&h=9f950bf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0f44f64227036f14d73276fb2f09f5c83d1edfe","tid":1422253,"uid":300692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab7746864bacb10f4b05b0679bb41b828233817e","tid":1422253,"uid":38189,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"似係nben條撚樣"},{"pid":"a4d1ce067be7e577ec5a4c350423103b140cd0e2","tid":1422253,"uid":24073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"將玩具向動物投擲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f1100f027f198668f407cc374b40f7c550ddc4","tid":1422253,"uid":29916,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ab7746864bacb10f4b05b0679bb41b828233817e","tid":1422253,"uid":38189,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"r